M|pre-dev-dependency-map|- Data Model passed Gate 5 validation
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|- About to select specific technologies
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|- Large Track workflow (2+ day features)
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|- Small Track workflow → skip to Task Breakdown
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|- Technologies already locked → skip to Task Breakdown
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|- Data Model not validated → complete Gate 5 first
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|**Runs before:** ring:pre-dev-task-breakdown
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|**Runs after:** ring:pre-dev-data-model
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|Every technology choice must be explicit, versioned, validated against Ring Standards, and justified. The Dependency Map answers WHAT specific products, versions, packages, and infrastructure will be 
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|Read `docs/pre-dev/{feature}/trd.md` — extract: `dpl.model`, `tech_stack.primary`, `project_technologies[]`.
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|If TRD metadata missing → STOP: "Go back to TRD (Gate 3) and complete Step 0.4."
