M|pre-dev-dependency-map|| Phase | Activities |
M|pre-dev-dependency-map||-------|------------|
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|| **1. Evaluation** | Ring Standards loaded; map TRD components to tech candidates; validate against Ring Standards; map Data Model to storage; map API contracts to protocols; check team expertise; es
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|| **2. Selection** | Per technology: check Ring Standards (mandatory/prohibited), specify exact version, list alternatives with trade-offs, verify compatibility, check sec (CVEs), validate licenses, c
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|| **3. Gate 6 Validation** | All dependencies explicit; no conflicts; no critical CVEs; licenses compliant; costs documented; all components mapped |
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|1. **Explicit**: `@v1.27.0` not `@latest` or `^1.0.0`
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|2. **Justified ranges**: If using `>=`, doc why
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|3. **Lock file referenced**: `go.mod`, `package-lock.json`, etc.
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|4. **Upgrade constraints**: doc why locked/capped
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|5. **Compatibility**: doc known conflicts
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|- Exact package names with versions (`go.uber.org/zap@v1.27.0`)
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|- Tech stack with constraints (`Go 1.24+, PostgreSQL 16`)
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|- Infrastructure specs (`Valkey 8, MinIO`)
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|- External SDKs, dev tools, sec deps, monitoring tools
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|- Compatibility matrices
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|- License summary
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|- Cost analysis
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|- Implementation code or how to use dependencies
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|- Task breakdowns or setup instructions
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|- Architectural patterns (→ TRD)
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|- Business requirements (→ PRD)
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|**File:** `docs/PROJECT_RULES.md`
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|**File:** `docs/pre-dev/{feature}/dependencies.md`
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|```markdown
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|| Category | PRD Requirement | Choice | Version | Rationale | Alternatives Considered |
M|pre-dev-dependency-map||----------|----------------|--------|---------|-----------|------------------------|
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|| Relational DB | Persistent user data | PostgreSQL | 16.2 | Ring standard; team expertise; ACID | MySQL (less preferred), SQLite (no concurrent writes) |
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|| Cache | ses storage | Valkey | 8.0 | Ring standard; Redis-compatible | Redis (licensing change) |
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|| Message Queue | Async processing | RabbitMQ | 3.13 | Ring standard; existing infra | Kafka (overkill for volume) |
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|| Package | Version | Lock File | Upgrade Constraint |
M|pre-dev-dependency-map||---------|---------|-----------|-------------------|
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|| go.uber.org/zap | v1.27.0 | go.sum | Stable API; no breaking changes in minor |
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|| Package | License | CVE Status | Risk |
M|pre-dev-dependency-map||---------|---------|-----------|------|
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|| github.com/jackc/pgx/v5 | MIT | None | Low |
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|| Component | Shared/Dedicated | Monthly Cost | Notes |
M|pre-dev-dependency-map||-----------|-----------------|-------------|-------|
