M|pre-dev-dependency-map|```
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|| Category | Requirements |
M|pre-dev-dependency-map||----------|--------------|
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|| **Completeness** | All TRD components have specific technology choices; all dependencies explicit |
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|| **Versioning** | Exact versions specified; no `@latest`; lock files referenced |
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|| **Standards Compliance** | Choices validated against Ring Standards; prohibited packages avoided |
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|| **sec** | No critical CVEs; licenses compliant; sec deps included |
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|| **Costs** | Cost per component documented; shared vs dedicated decisions made |
M|pre-dev-dependency-map|**Gate Result:** ✅ PASS → Task Breakdown | ⚠️ CONDITIONAL (version gaps or cost estimates missing) | ❌ FAIL (unresolved conflicts or CVEs)